sentence: Explore your SEKAI and look for materials!
Place the Natural Bed in your house.

Change your Gate to the Empty SEKAI Gate!

Go to Fledgling Field or Colorful Canyon and obtain 1 Comet Fragment.
Place the Astronomer's Observatory Telescope in your yard.
While outside, tap Layout and change your Weather settings.
Use your Gate to visit someone else's SEKAI.
Convert an item with a Converter!
Go to your Workbench, select Displays and build an item.
Select Merch on the Layout menu and place something.
Go to your Workbench, select Paintings and paint someone.
Make a Sketch in someone else's SEKAI!
When visiting another SEKAI, open the menu and select Sketch.
Take a photo and display it!
Select Camera on the menu and take a picture.
Go to your Workbench, select Displays and build a Photo Frame.
Select Small > Photos from Layout, and display your photo somewhere.
